user.currentRole: Strategy - Office of the CEO @ Cerebras
user.intro:
a bit late to the game but hello! i’m michelle, a rising junior at yale studying ethics, politics & economics and data science. some things about me are:
- i’m from dallas, tx but spent many childhood summers in southern China 
- **currently** taking a gap semester to travel around south korea. i’m working on a book that will be published next april and wrapping up a project, built an extension that analyzes news consumption.
- **always down** to brainstorm new project ideas & talk about echo ch
